      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once softened, add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) to the pan and cook for 30 secs or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 5,
