    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add your <strong>tomato paste</strong> with the <strong>chopped asparagus</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>double cream</strong> with your <strong>Chinese rice wine</strong>, <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>and the <strong>reserved starchy pasta water</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Cook for 2-3 min or until the asparagus is tender and the sauce has thickened – this is your <strong>garlic, chilli & cream sauce</strong></p>",
